Privacy

To see how many visitors use the site, this website uses PIWIK, an analytics tool. It uses cookies. No data is submitted to third parties and all IP addresses are made anonymous, so that it is not possible to draw conclusions to individual persons from data collected. You can choose not to be tracked any time by activating the Do-not-track function in your Browser settings.
